'''西恩·克里斯多福·史東'''（{{lang-en|Sean Christopher Stone}}，{{bd|1984年|12月29日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]演員、導演、製片人和電視節目主持人，名導[[奧利佛·史東|奧利佛·史東]]的兒子。

== 生平 ==
出生於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，是奧利佛·史東和伊莉莎白·伯基·考克斯（Elizabeth Burkit Cox）所生的兒子。

史東曾參演多部電影，其中包括了十幾部他父親執導的電影，如《[[火樂焚城|門]]》、《[[誰殺了甘迺迪|誰殺了甘迺迪]]》、《[[閃靈殺手|閃靈殺手]]》等<ref>{{Cite web|title=EXCLUSIVE: He sat on Michael Douglas' lap and co-starred with Kevin Costner in JFK but Sean Stone - son of director Oliver Stone – says getting his first kiss in the back of an Olds while playing Jim Morrison in hit movie was the best|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5845091/Oliver-Stones-son-Sean-reveals-like-growing-famous-director-father.html|accessdate=2021-01-08|date=2018-06-15|last=West|first=Ryan Parry|work=Mail Online|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616025301/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5845091/Oliver-Stones-son-Sean-reveals-like-growing-famous-director-father.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年2月，史東在[[伊朗|伊朗]]拍攝紀錄片時信奉[[什葉派|什葉派]][[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]，一時間成為媒體關注的焦點<ref>{{Cite web|title=Oliver Stone's Son Tells Bill O'Reilly That Mahmoud Ahmadinejad is 'A Little Bit Misunderstood' (Video)|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oliver-stone-sean-stone-bill-oreilly-mahmoud-ahmadinejad-293205|accessdate=2021-01-08|date=2012-02-21|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201144238/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oliver-stone-sean-stone-bill-oreilly-mahmoud-ahmadinejad-293205|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Famed Director's Son Converts To Islam|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/sean-stone-oliver-stone-son-convert-islam-iran_n_1276389|accessdate=2021-01-08|date=2012-02-14|work=HuffPost|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212084348/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/sean-stone-oliver-stone-son-convert-islam-iran_n_1276389|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.sky.com/home/showbiz-news/article/16173541|title=Oliver Stone's Son Wants To Help US With Islam|date=2012-02-20|work=Sky News|accessdate=2021-01-09|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223015855/http://news.sky.com/home/showbiz-news/article/16173541|archivedate=2012-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自2015年起，西恩·史東和泰瑞·溫圖拉（Tyrel Ventura）（前[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]州長[[傑西·溫圖拉|傑西·溫圖拉]]的兒子）和塔貝莎·華萊士（Tabetha Wallace）在{{le|RT美國台|RT America}}上共同主持節目《Watching the Hawks》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Jesse Ventura's Son And Oliver Stone's Son Get A Show At Russia Today|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/rosiegray/jesse-venturas-son-and-oliver-stones-get-a-show-at-russia-to|accessdate=2021-01-08|date=2015-03-09|publisher=BuzzFeed News|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412012301/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/rosiegray/jesse-venturas-son-and-oliver-stones-get-a-show-at-russia-to|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

